name: PCA

name: U.S. Map
requests: Create a U.S. map.

name: Bioinformatics - genes

name: Bioinformatics - length

name: Boxplot, ggplot2
requests: Create a boxplot of highway vs. type. Color by type. Add jitter points.

name: Boxplot, plotnine
requests: Use the plotnine package to create a boxplot of highway vs. type. Color by type.

name: Distribution (D): Numers
requests: Show me the distribution of highway.

name: Distribution (D): Numers
requests: Plot the distribution of highway.

name: D: normality
requests: Is city normally distributed?

name: D: Categories
requests: Show me the distribution of type as a barchart.

name: D: Categories, pie
requests: Create a pie chart based on type.

name: Relationship (R): Numbers-numbers
requests: Plot the relationship between highway and city.

name: R: Scatter with trend line
requests: Plot the relationship between highway and city. Add trend line. Add the R value on the plot.

name: R: Scatter, facets
requests: Plot the relationship between highway and city. Add trend line. Split into facets by cylinder.

name: R: Refined scatter plot
requests: Plot highway vs. city, colored by type. Change shape by drive. Change size by dis. Change x label to 'Highway mpg'. Change y label to 'City mpg'. Change background to white. Increase font for labels to 15. Remove all grids.

name: R: interactive scatter plot
requests: Use plotly to create an interactive scatter plot of city vs. dis. Change color by type.

name: R: Refined scatter plot
requests: Use the plotnine package. Plot highway vs. city, colored by type. Change shape by drive. Change size by dis. Change x label to 'Highway mpg'. Change y label to 'City mpg'. Change background to white. Increase font for labels to 15. Remove all grids.

name: R: Correlation coefficient
requests: Calculate the correlation coefficient of city vs highway. Repeat that after log transformation. Collect these results and show them.

name: R: Correlation coefficient
requests: Calculate the correlation coefficient of city and highway.

name: R: 3D scatter plot
requests: Use plotly to create a 3-D scatter plot with highway, city, and dis. Color by type.

name: R: Numbers-categories
requests: Show the relationship between highway and year as a boxplot. Color by year. Split by type. Flip the axes. Add jitter points.

name: R: Average by group
requests: Calculate the average highway MPG by type and year. Show it as a table with the rows are type and the columns are year.

name: R: Numbers-categories, density
requests: Only keep 4, 6, and 8 cylinderinders. Create a density plot of city, colored by year. Split into panels with one column by cylinder.

name: R: Compare among categories
requests: Create a plot to compare the fuel efficiency between automatic vs. manual transmission on the highway.

name: R: Density plot
requests: Only keep 4, 6, and 8 cylinderinders. Create a density plot of city, colored by year. Split into panels with one column by cylinder. Use the plotnine package.

name: R: violin plot
requests: Create a violin plot of city vs. type. Color by type. Add data points with jitter.

name: R: violin plot
requests: Create a violin plot of city vs. type. Color by type. Add data points with jitter. Use the plotnine package.

name: R: Category-category
requests: Are drive and cylinder independent?

name: R: Stacked barplot
requests: Plot the distribution of type as a barplot. Color by cylinder.

name: R: Category-category, plot
requests: Plot the combinations of drive and cylinder.

name: R: Category-category, mosaic
requests: Plot the combinations of drive and cylinder as a mosaic plot.

name: Multivariate (M): Correlation heatmap
requests: Create a correlation map of all the columns that contain numbers.

name: M: Hierarchical clustering
requests: Conduct hierarchical clustering.

name: M: ANOVA
requests: Conduct ANOVA of log-transformed highway by type and drive.

name: M: Regression
requests: Build a regression model of highway based on cylinder, dis, drive, and type. Give me diagnostic plots.

name: M: Neural network
requests: Build a neural network model to predict highway based on dis, cylinder, and type. Use the nnet package. Plot the distribution of residuals.

name: Data analysis
requests: Calculate average city by year and type. Then create a barplot of average mpg by type, colored by year. The bars for different years should be side by side.

name: Data analysis
requests: Calculate average city by year and type. Then use plotnine to create a barplot of average mpg by type, colored by year. The bars for different years should be side by side.

name: Convert data types
requests: Convert cylinder as numeric and calculate its correlation coefficient with highway.

name: Data processing
requests: highway and city represent miles per gallon (MPG) on the highway and in the city, respectively. Only keep cars more efficient than 15 MPG, but less than 40, on the highway. Add 0.5 to city MPG for correction. Perform log transformation on city MPG. Raise highway MPG to the second power. Calculate correlation coefficient of the two transformed variables.

name: Data wrangling, base R
requests: The dataset contains information about cars. Remove everything after \"(\" in transmissioncolumn. Remove cars labeled as 2seater in type. Define a new column called ratio by dividing highway by city. Plot ratio vs. highway. Color by type. Change marker type by trans. Change marker size by cylinder.

name: Data wrangling, base R
requests: The dataset contains information about cars. Remove everything after \"(\" in transmissioncolumn. Remove cars labeled as 2seater in type. Define a new column called ratio by dividing highway by city. Use plotnine to plot ratio vs. highway. Color by type. Change marker type by trans. Change marker size by cylinder.

name: Data wrangling, dplyr
requests: The dataset contains various about cars. First, use dplyr to prepare the data. Remove everything after \"(\" in transmissioncolumn. Remove cars labeled as 2seater in type. Define a new column called ratio by dividing highway by city. Sort the cars by ratio, highest first. Second, use the new data to plot ratio vs. highway. Color by type. Change marker type by trans. Change marker size by cylinder.

name: Interactive plots
requests: Plot highway vs. dis. Group by cylinder. Make it interactive with ggplotly.

name: Hindi, हिन्दी भाषा

name: barplot, English
requests: Remove data points belonging to the year of 1999. Define a new column ratio by dividing highway by city. Calculate averagey ratio by type. Create a barplot of average ratio vs. type. Label the y axis as 'Highway / city mpg ratio'.

name: barplot, En español
requests: Eliminar puntos de datos pertenecientes al year de 1999. Defina una nueva relación de columna dividiendo highway por city. Calcule el promedio de ratio por type. Cree un gráfico de barras de ratio promedio frente a type. Etiquete el eje y como 'Proporción de mpg en carretera/ciudad'.

name: barplot, 中文
requests: highway和city栏是高速和市区的每加仑里程数。year栏是车的生产年份。type栏是车行型的分类。删除 1999 年 的车。通过将 highway 除以 city 来定义新的列 ratio。计算各车型平均 ratio。创建平均 ratio与 车型的条形图。将 y 轴标记为‘高速公路/城市 mpg 比率’。

name: Barplot, 日本語
requests: highway 列と city 列には、高速道路または都市での MPG での燃料効率が含まれています。,year欄は車の製造年です。type列は、車両のタイプを指定します。1999 年に生産された車両を削除します。高速道路を都市の MPG で割って、比率という新しい列を定義します。typeごとの平均比率を計算します。平均比率対typeの棒グラフを作成します。 Y 軸に高速道路/都市の mpg 比」というラベルを付けます。

name: Barplot, deutsche Sprache
requests: Die Spalten highway und city enthalten Kraftstoffeffizienz in MPG auf der Autobahn oder in der Stadt. Die Jahresspalte ist das Baujahr des Autos. Die Spalte Klasse gibt den Fahrzeugtyp an. Entfernen Sie Fahrzeuge, die 1999 hergestellt wurden. Definieren Sie eine neue Spalte mit dem Namen Verhältnis, indem Sie Autobahn durch MPG der Stadt dividieren. Berechnen Sie das durchschnittliche Verhältnis nach Klasse. Erstellen Sie ein Balkendiagramm des durchschnittlichen Verhältnisses gegenüber der Klasse.

name: Barplot, Français
requests: Les colonnes highway et city contiennent le rendement énergétique en MPG sur l'autoroute ou en ville. La colonne année est l'année de production de la voiture. La colonne de typee précise le type de véhicule. Supprimez les véhicules produits en 1999. Définissez une nouvelle colonne appelée ratio en divisant l'autoroute par la ville MPG. Calculer le ratio moyen par typee. Créez un diagramme à barres du rapport moyen par rapport à la typee.

name: Barplot, Italiano
requests: Le colonne highway e city contengono l'efficienza del carburante in MPG in autostrada o in città. La colonna dell'anno è l'anno di produzione dell'auto. La colonna della typee specifica il tipo di veicolo. Rimuovi i veicoli prodotti nel 1999. Definisci una nuova colonna chiamata ratio dividendo l'autostrada per MPG della città. Calcola il rapporto medio per typee. Crea un grafico a barre del rapporto medio rispetto alla typee.

name: Barplot, हिन्दी भाषा
requests: हाईवे और सीटी कॉलम में हाईवे या शहर में एमपीजी में ईंधन दक्षता होती है। वर्ष स्तंभ कार के उत्पादन का वर्ष है। वर्ग स्तंभ वाहन के प्रकार को निर्दिष्ट करता है। 1999 में निर्मित वाहनों को हटा दें। शहर एमपीजी द्वारा राजमार्ग को विभाजित करके अनुपात नामक एक नया कॉलम परिभाषित करें। वर्ग द्वारा औसत अनुपात की गणना करें। औसत अनुपात बनाम वर्ग का एक बारप्लॉट बनाएँ।

name: Barplot, Luxembourgish
requests: D'highway an city Kolonnen enthalen Brennstoffeffizienz am MPG op der Autobunn oder an der Stad. D'year Kolonn ass d'Joer vun der Produktioun vum Auto. D'type Kolonn spezifizéiert den Typ vum Gefier. Ewechzehuelen Gefierer produzéiert an 1999. Definéieren eng nei Kolonn genannt ratio vun Autobunne vun Stad MPG opzedeelen. Berechent duerchschnëttlech ratio duerch type. Schafen eng barplot vun Moyenne ratio vs type.

name: Barplot, Ukrainian
requests: Стовпці highway і city містять економію палива в милях на галон на шосе чи в місті. Стовпець year — це рік виробництва автомобіля. Стовпець type визначає тип автомобіля. Вилучіть транспортні засоби, випущені в 1999 році. Визначте новий стовпець під назвою ratio, розділивши автомагістраль на кількість міст на галон. Обчисліть середнє значення ratio за type. Створіть бардіаграму середнього ratio проти type.

name: Total Counts

name: Boxplot, log
requests: Add 1 to all numbers and then conduct log transformation. Create a bloxplot of all columns.

name: Heatmap of variable genes
requests: Each row represents a gene. Each column is a sample. Remove genes with sum less than 10. Add 1 to all numbers. Log transform using base 2. Rank genes by standard deviations in descending order. Convert data as matrix. Subtract row means from all rows. Create a heatmap of the top 50 genes using red and green colors.

name: DESeq2
requests: Each row represents a gene. Each column is a sample. Remove rows with sum less than 10. Then use DESeq2 to identify differentially expressed genes. The first three columns are control samples. The last three are mutant. Show me the numbers of up and down-regulated genes based on FDR < 0.05 and log fold change > 1 or less than -1.
